Frontend: React.js (UI layer)
Backend: Node.js with Express (server-side logic, API handling)
State Management: Redux (managing global state in frontend)
Routing: React Router (handling navigation in frontend)
HTTP Client: Axios (making API calls from frontend to backend)
Development Server: Vite (frontend dev server running on port 5173)
Backend Server: Express (backend server running on port 7777)


~/devtinder-web$ git pull
~/devtinder-web$ npm run build
~/devtinder-web$ sudo scp -r ./dist/* /var/www/html/
~/devtinder-web$  service nginx status
~/devtinder$ pm2 start npm -- start
~/devtinder$ pm2 list 
~/devtinder$ pm2 log 
~/devtinder$ pm2 restart 0 
~/devtinder$ pm2 flush